<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/mar/25/">&#x27a0;</a> March 25, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="remote-buddy" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.iospirit.com/remotebuddy/">Products &gt; Remote Buddy</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Tool to enable use of the Apple Remote in more apps than just Front Row on OS X.  I hooked my old PowerPC Mac Mini up to a USB IR receiver, and can now control VLC with the Apple Remote that came with my MacBookPro.  Hoorah!  Well worth €10.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
                    Filed under
                    
