    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="bill-gates-vista-and-apples" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/16934083/site/newsweek/page/2/">Bill Gates on Vista and Apple&#39;s &#39;Lying&#39; Ads - Newsweek Technology - MSNBC.com</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Bill Gates trolls the Apple fanboy.  &#8220;Nowadays, security guys break the Mac every single day. Every single day, they come out with a total exploit, your machine can be taken over totally. I dare anybody to do that once a month on the Windows machine.&#8221;  I had to double-check this wasn&#8217;t some &#8220;Fake Steve&#8221;-style spoof!</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
