<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/jan/11/">&#x27a0;</a> January 11, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="crashplan" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.crashplan.com/">CrashPlan</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Impressive looking network backup software.  Straightforward to set-up, you can either pay CrashPlan to backup to their servers, or use local or friends&#8217; hard drives for free.  Lots of nice touches, like using Bonjour to discover local backup destinations automatically.  Once the Linux client is ready, I&#8217;ll be in heaven.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
